text: Sophia Vandagne (born 2 November 1979) is a Seychellois former weightlifter and Olympian. Competing in the women's 58 kg event at the 2000 Summer Olympics in Sydney, Sophia finished in thirteenth position with a total weight lifted of 160 kg. In 1999, Vandagne was nominated Seychellois Young Female Athlete of the year. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Seychellois female weightlifters Category:Olympic weightlifters of Seychelles Category:Weightlifters at the 2000 Summer Olympics
